column5: Grabbed my first coffee this morning and went outside to only find that I had 2 guys fishing from my dock...I decided to let them stay for a while because they were pretty quiet!
That's a really nice pic. Don't go walking barefoot on the dock eh?
Thanks Roy.....I'm just hoping there are no surprises all over my boat cover

Years ago at Big Gull Lake my wife was drinking coffee in the morning while I was out  fishing, she got to witness a blue heron grab and eat a red squirrel while it was screaming as it was swallowed whole.
At least they didn't have a white bucket.
What? And you didn't take out the shot gun?LOL
Wow, you would think a red squirrel would see a great blue! My jaw would drop watching that!
